                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On February 19, <persName corresp="#p_CJ1">Caffery</persName> reported that as he
                    left <persName corresp="#p_SR1">Schuman</persName>’s office, the French Foreign
                    Minister had remarked that he had come around to agreeing in general with the
                    United States ideas on the occupation statute. (Telegram 726, from Paris, not
                    printed, 740.00119 Control (Germany)/2–1949.)</p>
            </div>
